Now is the right time to backup your Rekordbox library.
It is highly recommended that you backup your Rekordbox library before any use of this program.
PRACT OBS connects to your Rekordbox library and it is possible, however unlikely, that it corrupts it. To prevent any loss of information including playlists, tracks, beatgrids, cue points, etc, run a library backup with the following option :
